cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper is about deep reinforcement learning and visual perception, which are both topics that fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of generative models (cs.AI) and visual inputs (cs.CV) to understand and probe the learned agents. Additionally, the experiments involve environments and simulations (cs.RO) and the potential applications of this technique include AI safety (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, and cs.SY.
